# Copy to .env.local (gitignored) and fill your BYOK keys for dev.
# .env.local is ignored by git (*.local) and the env-read path is DEV-gated,
# so production builds never inline keys. Only VITE_LLM_KEY / VITE_STT_KEY are
# required to exercise AI classify + final STT; the URL/model overrides below
# are optional (seed has working DeepSeek + Paraformer defaults).

VITE_LLM_KEY=
VITE_STT_KEY=
# VITE_LLM_URL=
# VITE_LLM_MODEL=
# VITE_STT_MODEL=

# 使用反馈：开发期内置 GitHub PAT（fine-grained，仅 issues:write + gists:write，
# 限 AiJi 仓库，90 天过期）。Vite 构建时 inline 进包 → APK 自带，终端用户零配置。
# .env.local (gitignored) 填真实值；本文件仅占位。正式版前迁 CF Worker（见
# docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-19-feedback-feature-design.md §2）。
VITE_FEEDBACK_GITHUB_TOKEN=
VITE_FEEDBACK_GITHUB_REPO=
